{"type": "article", "id": 29961, "title": "手工制作的铅笔", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-21T23:01:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160721212319qOcyMRm02JXtdu4B.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>和其他书写工具相比，别出心裁的铅笔设计似乎有些少见。来自意大利的 Sotterranea Officina Sperimentale 工作室最近推出了一款名为 Sostanza 的铅笔，不管是造型还是功能都让人颇为惊艳。这些铅笔都采用精选自世界各地的天然木材，以手工制作的方式在意大利进行小批量生产。铅笔本身仅由重量极轻的笔套和用来固定的圆环两部分组成，外形采用了符合人体工程学的设计，带给人流畅的书写体验。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1417483388/sostanza\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 25 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721212338HkTM913Wf2yp4FGw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721212339KwhoFpejJ8ldyrC0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721212339VeKyIiaOGRD5T89u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607212123397mJCghVEBfxtqrRF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}